# blog/

A comprehensive blog series documenting the Intent methodology, from foundational philosophy through practical implementation and AI integration. The series explores how intention-aware development improves code quality, team onboarding, and LLM collaboration.

## Files

- `README.md` -- Index and overview of the blog series with key concepts
- `0000-motivation-for-intent.md` -- Foundational exploration of why intention matters in modern software development
- `0001-introduction-to-intent.md` -- Practical introduction to Intent as a solution for intention-aware development
- `0002-the-steel-thread-methodology.md` -- Core methodology: what steel threads are and how they preserve intent through development
- `0003-intent-capture-in-software-development.md` -- Techniques for capturing, documenting, and preserving developer intention
- `0004-llm-collaboration-with-intent.md` -- How Intent's structure transforms AI assistance and multiplies development capabilities
- `0005-getting-started-with-intent.md` -- Installation, setup, and daily workflow guide with real examples
- `0006-next-steps-and-future-work.md` -- Evolution roadmap, current state assessment, and lessons learned
- `0007-intent-agents-supercharge-claude.md` -- Intent v2.1.0 agent system for persistent Claude Code collaboration
